videos.description: John O'Korn sacked by Mike Barwick Jr. for a loss of 8 yards to the Ind 38
videos.headline: O'Korn having trouble early against Indiana

videos.description: Jordan Glasgow blocks Indiana's punt early in the second quarter to set up Michigan inside the Hoosiers' 45-yard line.
videos.headline: Michigan blocks Indiana punt to set up good field position

videos.description: De'Veon Smith run for 25-yards to the Ind 11 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Michigan keeps drive alive with big run on 4th down

videos.description: Kenny Allen 28-yard FG GOOD
videos.headline: Michigan gets the first points of the game on a 28-yard field goal

videos.description: Camion Patrick runs for a 2-yard touchdown to put the Hoosiers on the board in the second quarter against Michigan.
videos.headline: Indiana's Patrick runs untouched into the end zone

videos.description: John O'Korn's early strugles against Indiana
videos.headline: John O'Korn's early strugles against Indiana

videos.description: Indiana head coach Kevin Wilson talks about his teams great defensive first half giving them a 7-3 halftime lead
videos.headline: Indiana head coach Kevin Wilson talks about his teams great defensive first half giving them a 7-3 halftime lead

videos.description: Kenny Allen 33-yard FG GOOD
videos.headline: Michigan hits 33-yard FG to cut deficit to 1

videos.description: In the third quarter, Indiana extends its lead with Griffin Oakes' 24-yard field goal.
videos.headline: Indiana's Oakes puts through 24-yard field goal

videos.description: John O'Korn run for 30-yards to the Ind 34 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: John O'Korn run for 30-yards for a 1ST down

videos.description: Michigan takes the lead over Indiana thanks to De'Veon Smith's 34-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Smith dives at the pylon for Michigan TD

videos.description: De'Veon Smith has taken over in the second half, scoring another touchdown in the final seconds of the third quarter.
videos.headline: Smith strikes again with another Michigan TD

videos.description: Jordan Glasgow blocks Indiana's punt in the fourth quarter, marking Michigan's second blocked punt of the game.
videos.headline: Michigan blocks second punt of the game

videos.description: Michigan converts 4th down to keep drive alive
videos.headline: Michigan converts 4th down to keep drive alive

videos.description: Michigan QB John O'Korn talks about the team's attitude and effort in grinding out a 20-10 win over Indiana.
videos.headline: Michigan QB John O'Korn talks win over Indiana
